# from src/main.rs on the sergi0g/cup tip — clap `#[derive(Parser/
# Subcommand)]` macros (Cli + Commands enums) parsed exactly as
# declared.  Cfg-gated subcommands (`check` requires the `cli` feature,
# `serve` requires the `server` feature) are both included because the
# default Cargo features `["server", "cli"]` enable both — virtually
# every distribution / package-manager build ships with both available.
#
