#                         HEAD requests against each image's registry;
#                         `cup serve` mode adds an embedded web UI +
#                         tokio-cron-scheduler-driven periodic refresh
#                         with Discord/Slack/Generic webhook
#                         notifications; 1307★ AGPL-3.0)
#                 _cup             [Rust=242 OPENS Axis 187, 1/0/0]
#                                                  ↑↑↑ THIS FILE ↑↑↑
#
#     Go      : (next round — Go=242, slot 2/0/0)
#                Canonical Go cron scheduler: github.com/robfig/cron by
#                Rob Figueiredo — the de-facto standard "cron in Go"
